yle=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\">&lt;/script&gt;</span>&nbsp;</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#323232;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">194</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\">&lt;/body&gt;</span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr style=\"background-color:#1b2426;\" valign=\"top\">\n			<td style=\"border:0px; border-right-color:#435a5f; border-right-width:3px; color:#b9bdb6; border-right-style:solid; text-align:right; padding-right:5px; width:40px;\">195</td>\n			<td style=\"border:0px; padding-left:10px; text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:#5ba1cf\">&lt;/html&gt;</span></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">有点快闪这种行为艺术的感觉，最互联网的地方似乎就是需要微信支付吧~在O2O的风口，却并不上门服务，还在商场里开连锁店。 所以上门，还是实体店？哪种才是玩转美业的正确姿势？</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">至于，这些项目的创始人以及核心高管，会到现场问什么问题，诊断官们又会给出什么解答，这些老中医我都不知道。还要你自己来现场看呢！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">罗辑思维联合创始人吴声、著名投资人李丰、唱吧创始人兼CEO陈华</span>&mdash;&mdash;会在本文见光之后，每人认领一个项目，作为主诊医生。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">导师和项目，你希望看到什么样的配对？留言说出你的想法啊，但是他们并不会听你的。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">太任性！所以，我还要邀请了由三位创业者、三位自媒体组成的观察团来帮腔，既不能成了导师的一言堂，也不能成了创业项目安利产品的宣讲堂。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">我老中医的场子，就是要针尖对麦芒，要逼你讲真话，要句句戳痛点！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">我嗅老中医，不让吹牛逼。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">等你呢，<a href=\"http://www.huxiu.com/shop?f=article?f=article\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(52, 140, 223); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; -webkit-transition: all 0.2s; background-color: transparent;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">快报名来吧</span></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">~</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">活动地点：造物空间</span>（北京东城区地安门东大街89号左右时代四层，地铁南锣鼓巷地铁E口，乘电梯直达）<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">活动时间：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">2015年7月26日下午13:30~17:30</span>（13:30开始签到，14:00正式开始）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">现场仅开放99席围观名额，尚有余位，预来从速哦~每位围观费用：299软妹币。购票的你还能<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">获赠吴声新书《场景革命》 以及限量版纪念笔记本，and吴老师新书现场签名机会</span>呢。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">末了，感谢下合作推广的小伙伴活动行，活动树和微链。以及造物空间的场地，还有现场美美的茶歇诺心蛋糕，Why not手冲咖啡。对的，并没有面包和生鲜可以吃哦。严！</span></p>\n', '2015-06-11 14:36:31', '2015-07-28 01:45:36', '1', '北邮,中国互联网', '1', '0', '1', '2', 'resource/content/2015/06/11/201506111829250.jpg', '1', '1', '1', '5', '1', '1', 'pages/c/2015/07/27/3RS6aKIWz.html', '中国互联网', '北邮知名校友张春江死缓期间没有犯罪，获减刑', '提到北邮和中国互联网，总会让人想起什么', '1', null, null, null, null, '0', '480', '600', null);
INSERT INTO `keke_content` VALUES ('12', '潭州学院Keke老师购物车的实现', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(154, 162, 173); font-size: 13px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\">有点快闪这种行为艺术的感觉，最互联网的地方似乎就是需要微信支付吧~在O2O的风口，却并不上门服务，还在商场里开连锁店。 所以上门，还是实体店？哪种才是玩转美业的正确姿势？</p>\n\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(154, 162, 173); font-size: 13px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\">至于，这些项目的创始人以及核心高管，会到现场问什么问题，诊断官们又会给出什么解答，这些老中医我都不知道。还要你自己来现场看呢！</p>\n\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(154, 162, 173); font-size: 13px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">罗辑思维联合创始人吴声、著名投资人李丰、唱吧创始人兼CEO陈华</span>&mdash;&mdash;会在本文见光之后，每人认领一个项目，作为主诊医生。</p>\n\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(154, 162, 173); font-size: 13px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\">导师和项目，你希望看到什么样的配对？留言说出你的想法啊，但是他们并不会听你的。</p>\n\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(154, 162, 173); font-size: 13px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; font-family: STHeiti, Arial, \'Microsoft Yahei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Simsun,sans-self\'; line-height: 28px;\">太任性！所以，我还要邀请了由三位创业者、三位自媒体组成的观察团来帮腔，既不能成了导师的一言堂，也不能成了创业项目安利产品的宣讲堂。</p>\n\n<p style=\"word-